        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "O thou false accuser, or slanderer, or whosoever thou art, that art guilty of any such like practices? ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Sharp arrows of the mighty —",
